tiquiliae

0.30–0.33?, 0.33– 0.40/), more produced anteocular portion of the head (0.30–0.34?, 0.34–0.41/; 

tiquiliae

0.26–0.30?, 0.29–0.36/), and longer labium (1.85–2.30?, 1.93–2.48/; 

tiquiliae

1.50– 1.85?, 1.66–1.95/).
